===Etymology===
From the context of a game of baseball being constrained to the ballpark it was played at.

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[ballpark]] [[figure]]}}

#{{idiom}} [[colloquial]] (USA) An [[educated]] [[guess]] or [[estimation]] within [[acceptable]] [[bound]]s.
